title: 'Sit still and do nothing': Trump's latest tariff salvos leave markets unfazed
summary_full: Asia stocks were mostly higher, safe-haven assets stayed firm, with yield on the 10-year U.S. Treasury little changed, while gold inched about 1% higher.
